<section class="admissions-journey">
  <h2>Our Admissions Journey</h2>

  <div class="step">
    <h3>1. Book an Individual Tour</h3>
    <p>We personalize our school tours for each family, recognizing that every child and parent has unique interests and questions. Your visit can be as short or as in-depth as you prefer—just let us know. After your tour, you’ll have the opportunity for an informal conversation with our Headmaster, Mr James Featherstone.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta-link">Click here to arrange a School Tour &gt;&gt;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <h3>2. Taster Day</h3>
    <p>We’ll arrange a taster day for your child(ren) to experience life at SHICS. These days are scheduled according to your child’s current school year and, like our tours, are tailored to your family’s needs and your child’s interests. For more details, contact our Admissions Manager: admissions@extercs.org | 01392 255 298</p>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <h3>3. Registration Form</h3>
    <p>You may complete the registration form at any point in the admissions process, though we suggest submitting it after your child’s taster day. A £90 non-refundable registration fee secures your child’s place at SHICS.</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta-link">Click here to Register your child &gt;&gt;</a>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <h3>4. Offer Letter</h3>
    <p>After the taster day, a member of our Senior Leadership Team will review the feedback, school report, and reference before deciding whether to offer your child(ren) a place at SHICS.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <h3>5. Acceptance Form</h3>
    <p>Once you receive an offer letter and wish to proceed, you’ll be asked to complete an acceptance form. A £250 confirmation deposit will be held on your account until your child leaves SHICS. We look forward to officially welcoming your family and supporting your child(ren) on their special learning journey at SHICS.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="cta-box">
    <h3>Book an Individual Tour Today</h3>
    <p>Start your personalized learning journey at SHICS!</p>
    <a href="#" class="cta-button">Book an Individual Tour</a>
  </div>
</section>